Titolo: Mutant Night

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Mutant Night is an arcade platform shooter game released in 1987 by UPL. The player controls a small white creature named Mutron-kun. The creature has a large eye that the bubbles can be shot from.These bubbles then kill the various and diverse enemies that attack, for example skeletal monkeys, space ships and spinning discs. Mutron-kun also has the ability to jump and remain floating for a period of time by the repeated pressing of the jump button.